data.description: NEW PRICE NEW TERMS: Preferred lender will offer a 1 YEAR 1% RATE BUYDOWN AND $600 APPRAISAL CREDIT to qualified buyer with an acceptable offer. So, do you have horses, alpacas or even donkeys? 4 wheelers? Need a huge shop? A beautiful home with 180 views of Green Mtn, Scraggy Peak and Buffalo Peak? Hummingbird Hill Ranch has it all. Approaching through a gated entry to a paved drive, this stunning home sits on over 11 usable acres and features an open floor plan with a true Great Room. A wall of windows brings the outdoors in along with that view, and the large deck is ideal for entertaining or just winding down after a long day. Log accents and beams give a beautiful finish and a knook with woodstove serves as either additional office space or a cozy spot to curl up with a good book. Mud room from the attached main garage leads past main floor laundry and pantry before heading into the open kitchen. Continuing on the main floor is a home office, a powder room, a lovely primary suite with mountain views, soaking tub, large walk in shower. Heading upstairs you'll find two bedrooms with a connecting full bath. Downstairs to the walkout lower level and you have another generous guest room with mountain views plus a media room with screen and projector included. From the media room opens a door into the 2nd garage, tucked under around the back with paved driveway access. One garage door & one man door provide access to this oversized garage with plenty of room for a small second vehicle, utility vehicles, or plow. Outside, the land itself is spectacular with well mitigated space, pastures featuring a fully fenced perimeter, a fenced paddock off the 3 stall barn, and cross fenced with two pasture areas, all easily reconfigured to meet your needs. In addition to the barn, greenhouse, chicken coop, the star of the outbuilding show is the new 2400 square foot steel shop with four 12x14 doors for large equipment or RV access. Copy/Paste Tour: https://vimeo.com/835843672
